---
title: Garth Greenhand
---

King Garth Gardener, better known as Garth Greenhand, was the legendary first King of the Reach and founder of House Gardener.

Legend: According to legend, Garth Greenhand was the first member of the First Men family to rule the Reach. He supposedly wore a crown of vines and flowers and made the land bloom. Garth had many descendents, supposedly half the noble houses in the Reach, including the Tyrells and the Florents, can trace their lineage back to him.


